{"word":"Σκαριώτης","slug":"Σκαριώτης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>Σϰαριώτης</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Heb.\">Heb.</a>] one of the spellings of the surname of the apostle Judas and his father, as <b><a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> in <b><a href='B:470 10:4'>Mt 10:4</a>; <a href='B:470 26:14'>26:14</a>; <a href='B:480 14:10'>Mk 14:10</a>.</b> S. <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:Ἰσκαριώθ\">Ἰσκαριώθ</a></el> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prec.\">prec.</a> entry. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:Σκαριώθ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:σκάφη\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}